---
// AccordionPreview.astro - Static preview of Accordion component
---

<div class="accordion-preview not-content">
  <div class="preview-section">
    <div class="preview-label">Accordion</div>
    <div class="accordion">
      <div class="accordion-item accordion-item-open">
        <button class="accordion-trigger">
          <span>What is SpinozaOS?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <p>SpinozaOS is a philosophy-driven, motion-first design system built for AGI-era applications. It provides design tokens, React components, and animation presets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger">
          <span>How do I install it?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-trigger">
          <span>Is it accessible?</span>
          <svg class="accordion-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="preview-section">
    <div class="preview-label">Variants</div>
    <div class="preview-row">
      <span class="variant-badge">default</span>
      <span class="variant-badge">bordered</span>
      <span class="variant-badge">ghost</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .accordion-preview {
    background: #020617;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .preview-section {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .preview-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .preview-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  .preview-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .accordion {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .accordion-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .accordion-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .accordion-trigger {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .accordion-trigger:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  }

  .accordion-icon {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: #64748b;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .accordion-item-open .accordion-icon {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .accordion-content {
    padding: 0 1rem 1rem;
  }

  .accordion-content p {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .variant-badge {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }
</style>
